cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.HC, cs.SY

This paper discusses the use of technology, specifically mobile phones, for contact tracing during an epidemic. It also highlights the privacy concerns associated with such technology. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
